          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/59680734/" class=" " title="Colorlesshome">Colorlesshome</a>
                (不彻底)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="43409522">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">人们在某些点上并不是确切地知道真理。完全的确实性只是人们的态度问题。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2017-04-26 14:37</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <p>人们在某些点上并不是确切地知道真理。完全的确实性只是人们的态度问题。</p>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







